{"text_id":141843,"tokens":["How"," to"," Treat"," Progressive"," Aph","asia","\n","Overview","\n","Progressive"," aph","asia"," is"," a"," condition"," in"," which"," a"," person"," loses"," the"," ability"," to"," speak"," or"," understand"," words"," or"," phrases"," over"," a"," period"," of"," time","."," The"," condition"," is"," often"," due"," to"," stroke"," or"," another"," issue"," affecting"," the"," brain",".","\n","A"," person"," with"," progressive"," aph","asia"," may"," be"," able"," to"," communicate"," using"," nonverbal"," methods"," such"," as"," facial"," expressions",","," gestures",","," and"," writing","."," As"," the"," condition"," gets"," worse",","," they"," may"," only"," be"," able"," to"," understand"," written"," words"," or"," phrases",".","\n","If"," you"," or"," a"," loved"," one"," is"," living"," with"," progressive"," aph","asia",","," there"," are"," several"," ways"," to"," improve"," communication"," and"," maintain"," quality"," of"," life",".","\n","Symptoms","\n","The"," symptoms"," of"," progressive"," aph","asia"," can"," vary"," from"," person"," to"," person"," but"," may"," include",":","\n","Having"," trouble"," remembering"," words"," or"," phrases","\n","Getting"," stuck"," on"," a"," word"," or"," phrase"," during"," speech","\n","Having"," difficulty"," understanding"," what"," others"," are"," saying","\n","Having"," difficulty"," reading"," or"," writing","\n","Losing"," the"," ability"," to"," speak",","," read",","," or"," write"," over"," time","\n"," Causes","\n","The"," cause"," of"," progressive"," aph","asia"," is"," often"," a"," stroke"," or"," another"," brain"," injury","."," It"," can"," also"," be"," caused"," by"," a"," chronic"," condition"," such"," as"," Parkinson","'","s"," disease",".","\n","If"," you"," have"," a"," stroke",","," you"," are"," more"," likely"," to"," develop"," progressive"," aph","asia"," if"," you"," are"," male",","," elderly",","," or"," have"," a"," history"," of"," stroke",".","\n","If"," you"," have"," progressive"," aph","asia",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," seek"," medical"," attention"," as"," soon"," as"," possible",".","\n","Diagnosis","\n","Progressive"," aph","asia"," is"," usually"," diagnosed"," by"," a"," speech","-","language"," pathologist"," or"," a"," neuro","logist",".","\n","They"," will"," likely"," ask"," you"," or"," your"," loved"," one"," about"," your"," symptoms"," and"," medical"," history","."," They"," may"," also"," perform"," a"," physical"," exam"," and"," order"," tests"," such"," as"," a"," MRI"," or"," CT"," scan"," to"," rule"," out"," other"," conditions",".","\n","Treatments","\n","There"," is"," no"," cure"," for"," progressive"," aph","asia",","," but"," there"," are"," treatments"," that"," can"," help"," improve"," communication"," and"," maintain"," quality"," of"," life",".","\n","Speech"," therapy",":"," A"," speech","-","language"," pathologist"," can"," help"," you"," or"," your"," loved"," one"," improve"," communication"," skills"," and"," learn"," nonverbal"," methods"," of"," communication",".","\n","Ass","istive"," technology",":"," There"," are"," many"," devices"," and"," apps"," that"," can"," help"," people"," with"," progressive"," aph","asia"," communicate"," more"," easily","."," These"," may"," include"," tablets",","," smartphones",","," or"," other"," devices"," that"," can"," be"," used"," to"," type"," or"," point"," to"," words",".","\n","Support"," groups",":"," Joining"," a"," support"," group"," can"," help"," you"," or"," your"," loved"," one"," connect"," with"," others"," who"," are"," living"," with"," progressive"," aph","asia","."," This"," can"," provide"," emotional"," support"," and"," help"," you"," learn"," about"," new"," treatments"," and"," resources",".","\n","Communication"," partner"," training",":"," This"," is"," a"," type"," of"," therapy"," that"," helps"," friends"," and"," family"," members"," better"," understand"," and"," communicate"," with"," someone"," with"," progressive"," aph","asia","."," It"," can"," also"," help"," reduce"," the"," stress"," and"," frustration"," that"," can"," come"," with"," caring"," for"," someone"," with"," the"," condition",".","\n","Living"," with"," Progressive"," Aph","asia","\n","Progressive"," aph","asia"," can"," make"," it"," difficult"," to"," communicate"," with"," others",","," but"," there"," are"," ways"," to"," improve"," communication"," and"," maintain"," quality"," of"," life",".","\n","If"," you"," or"," a"," loved"," one"," is"," living"," with"," progressive"," aph","asia",","," consider"," the"," following"," tips",":","\n","Use"," nonverbal"," methods"," of"," communication",":"," This"," may"," include"," facial"," expressions",","," gestures",","," and"," writing",".","\n","Use"," assis","tive"," technology",":"," There"," are"," many"," devices"," and"," apps"," that"," can"," help"," people"," with"," progressive"," aph","asia"," communicate"," more"," easily","."," These"," may"," include"," tablets",","," smartphones",","," or"," other"," devices"," that"," can"," be"," used"," to"," type"," or"," point"," to"," words",".","\n","Join"," a"," support"," group",":"," Joining"," a"," support"," group"," can"," help"," you"," or"," your"," loved"," one"," connect"," with"," others"," who"," are"," living"," with"," progressive"," aph","asia","."," This"," can"," provide"," emotional"," support"," and"," help"," you"," learn"," about"," new"," treatments"," and"," resources",".","\n","Commun","icate"," with"," your"," healthcare"," team",":"," Be"," sure"," to"," communicate"," with"," your"," healthcare"," team"," about"," your"," symptoms"," and"," any"," changes"," you"," are"," experiencing","."," This"," can"," help"," them"," provide"," the"," best"," possible"," care"," for"," you",".","\n","Keep"," up"," with"," your"," rehabilitation",":"," Continue"," to"," do"," any"," rehabilitation"," exercises"," or"," activities"," that"," you"," have"," been"," prescribed","."," This"," can"," help"," you"," maintain"," or"," improve"," your"," communication"," skills","."],"sub_source":"wikihow","model":"cohere","label":1}